sequenceDiagram
    actor Student
    participant IDE as Browser IDE
    participant Templates as ProjectCreator / project-template
    participant Gallery as gallery / scene editor
    participant AST as ProcedureEditor / AST modules
    participant Codegen as tweedle-codegen
    participant Runner as ProjectRunner / Tweedle VM
    participant Render as renderer

    Student->>IDE: create new project
    IDE->>Templates: createBlank() / createEmptyWorldProject()
    Templates-->>IDE: AliceProjectArchive

    Student->>Gallery: add biped
    Gallery->>IDE: append scene object / field
    IDE-->>Student: scene updated

    Student->>AST: write walk procedure
    AST->>AST: insert / reorder statements
    AST->>Codegen: generateTweedle(AST)
    Codegen-->>IDE: source preview

    Student->>IDE: run world
    IDE->>Runner: loadProject() / run()
    Runner->>Render: object + animation state
    Render-->>Student: running world preview
